| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3444 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 160c59ec-2ea6-58c1-b4a3-7b2a511cb0db"
